{"tid":2372150,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳肇始：恢復花市非所謂「轉彎」 而是平衡抗疫及各方訴求","createTime":"2021-01-19T11:54:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T12:08:23.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"7e35b8b689f595abaaf9667f007cad0ab473873e","tid":2372150,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:54:46.000Z","msg":"陳肇始：恢復花市非所謂「轉彎」 平衡抗疫及各方訴求<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局局長陳肇始表示，政府恢復年宵花市，並不構成所謂的「轉彎」，因為在本月8日宣布取消花市的新聞稿中已表示，當局會協助花農以其他方式籌備，亦會與花農見面，探討措施的可行性，她形容是經過一星期商討後的成果。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始表示，早前宣布取消花市是要讓花農及早知道，早些有另外的安排，她強調今次的決定已平衡抗疫及各方訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571260-20210119.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571260-20210119.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmeoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=d8b579e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571260-20210119.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=74159ab2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571260-20210119.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"d47d2510391e8fd57b499b74bf437fd5b28d1984","tid":2372150,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:55:20.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">👎</span>"},{"pid":"66349743f299e2c8eb309629cd22885b485e4231","tid":2372150,"uid":103230,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:57:05.000Z","msg":"之前先發晒爛渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來做奴材契弟真係咁冇尊嚴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10992a24172accf603280fdf892652d9291ea07f","tid":2372150,"uid":291865,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:57:45.000Z","msg":"D新界佬好惡架"},{"pid":"35dae7b58247ce4bfad4f5b